# Synthetic Episode Studio

Create consistent, traceable, export-ready synthetic NHS-style clinical episodes without exposing patient data.

> Synthetic demonstration data only. Not clinically validated, not for patient care, and not endorsed by the NHS.

Full setup, architecture, source and demo documentation is completed as part of the MVP release.
